{"total":20,"pageSize":8,"pageCount":3,"data":[{"title":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","slug":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","date":"2019-11-13T01:54:56.000Z","updated":"2019-11-13T02:09:00.052Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/build-linux-kenel-in-qumu.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"><a href=\"#在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"></a>在<code>QEMU</code>中运行编译的<code>Linux</code>内核</h1><h2 id=\"内核编译脚本-build-sh\"><a href=\"#内核编译脚本-build-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内核编译脚本 build.sh\"></a>内核编译脚本 <code>build.sh</code></h2><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export ARCH=arm</span><br><span class=\"line\">export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extra</span><br><span class=\"line\">export CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi-</span><br><span class=\"line\">make LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</span><br><span class=\"line\">make zImage -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make modules -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make dtbs</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/zImage extra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/dts/*ca9.dtb\textra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp .config extra/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li><p>默认的内核配置文件为 <code>LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</code>.上述脚本会将自动编译好的<code>zImage,dtbs</code>复制到<code>extra</code>目录中</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>extra</code>目录下的vexpress是一张虚拟的SD卡，作为<em>根文件系统</em>的存放介质。它能以<code>loop</code>形式被挂载<code>mount</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"编译模块的脚本-module-sh\"><a href=\"#编译模块的脚本-module-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译模块的脚本 module.sh\"></a>编译模块的脚本 <code>module.sh</code></h2><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules_install INSTALL_MOD_PATH=extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo umount extra/img</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li>它会自动编译内核模块并安装到<code>vexprees.img</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"启动带LCD的ARM-Linux内核\"><a href=\"#启动带LCD的ARM-Linux内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动带LCD的ARM Linux内核\"></a>启动带<code>LCD</code>的<code>ARM Linux</code>内核</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg\" alt=\"01-arm-linux-qemu-lcd.jpg\"></p>\n","text":"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核内核编译脚本 build.sh1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>export ARCH=arm<br>export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extr","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":1,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":1,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"}]},{"title":"funds","slug":"funds","date":"2019-03-29T15:17:18.000Z","updated":"2019-03-29T16:03:43.000Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/funds.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"从零开始的基金之路\"><a href=\"#从零开始的基金之路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"从零开始的基金之路\"></a>从零开始的基金之路</h1><p>人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。</p>\n<h2 id=\"根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"><a href=\"#根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"></a>根本准则 ： <code>追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格</code></h2><p>若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"从零开始的基金之路人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。此路缘何当作养成游戏的娱乐养成储蓄的习惯保持学","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"基金","slug":"基金","count":1,"path":"api/tags/基金.json"}]},{"title":"auto-google-translation","slug":"auto-google-translation","date":"2019-02-15T01:57:53.000Z","updated":"2019-02-15T02:08:28.118Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/auto-google-translation.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"字幕也疯狂\"><a href=\"#字幕也疯狂\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字幕也疯狂\"></a>字幕也疯狂</h1><p><code>观曲千首 不如操琴一曲</code> 试着做一个勤劳的字幕组小员工~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s28051018.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100%\"></p>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s28051018.jpg","content":null,"text":"字幕也疯狂观曲千首 不如操琴一曲 试着做一个勤劳的字幕组小员工~ [Figure] Bili链接","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":5,"path":"api/tags/python.json"},{"name":"script","slug":"script","count":1,"path":"api/tags/script.json"}]},{"title":"some_tools_in_computer","slug":"some-tools-in-computer","date":"2019-02-14T04:29:06.000Z","updated":"2019-02-15T02:12:39.516Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/some-tools-in-computer.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"龙套角色也精彩\"><a href=\"#龙套角色也精彩\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"龙套角色也精彩\"></a>龙套角色也精彩</h1><p>这是学习<a href=\"\">操作系统</a>时总结的一些编程开发工具，虽然这些并不是实实在在